## Summary
This documentation details the Extole destination integration with Amplitude, which enables streaming user behavior data to power customer-led growth initiatives like referral programs and challenges. The integration maps Amplitude user IDs to Extole email addresses, requires an Extole access token for setup, and allows filtering of events and properties to be sent.

